def generate_unique_subsets(nums):
    n = len(nums)
    nums.sort()
    ans = []

    def solve(i, temp):
        ans.append(temp[:])
        for j in range(i, n):
            if j > i and nums[j] == nums[j - 1]:
                continue
            temp.append(nums[j])
            solve(j + 1, temp)
            temp.pop()
    solve(1, [])
    return ans
